aju b´inchb´en te Seeker otoq tz´el t-xo´n tib´, extzen a Harry mya b´i´n twitz alkye
mas nya b´a´n — aye xjal n-chi kyq´ama´n te qa k-xel t-xnaq´tza´n moqa aye xjal n-chi kyq´ama´n te qa k-ok te
n-chi b´et t-xe t-xu´k n-chi tzaj t-xo´n jun colchón.
